Which of the following commands displays information about a given physical volume in anLVM setup?
A)  pvdisp
B)  pvlist
C)  pvdisplay
D)  pvl
C
C. The pvdisplay command shows information about a given physical volume. You canuse pvdisplay to view the device on which the PV is built along with the extent size of thePV. The other commands shown are not valid.Chapter 4: Troubleshooting (Domain 4.0)231
